description: SmoothJazz.com president, Sandy Shore, sits down with Grammy winning bassist, Stanley Clarke at the Rivera Maya Jazz Festival 2011 in Playa del Carmen Mexico to discuss his performance as well as his new record label Roxboro Entertainment Group.
